Trekking Time

Star Trek is a science fiction universe that goes far beyond the original TV series. Thus, it may be confusing to navigate such vast space without any guide. This webapp provides a item-based timeline of the events of the universe. This list reflects the understanding of the editors of the Memory Alpha website which was made with little inference.

Use the controls bellow to filter the items. Hover the mouse or touch the thumbnails to see details.
